message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.AI", "cs.LG", "cs.IR", and "cs.CY". The paper deals with generating a large-scale QA dataset for electronic medical records using NLP techniques, which falls under the scope of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves training baseline models for question to logical form and question to answer mapping, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves exploring the learning potential of the dataset, which can be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
